Package: finnix-netboot
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, whiptail, nfs-user-server | nfs-kernel-server, tftpd-hpa, portmap, module-init-tools (>= 3.9), syslinux | yaboot, isc-dhcp-client, perl, finnix-release
Description: Scripts to set up network booting in Finnix
 This package contains the finnix-netboot-* scripts, which are designed 
 to build an host a netboot environment for booting Finnix over a 
 network.
